.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 2020-NOV-18 GNU

.SH NAME
simple_shell \- shell terminal in C language

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh
.TP
[\fBecho\fR \fIcommand\fR] | ./hsh

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B simple_shell
.TP
This program runs a shell interface using C programming, it will handle regular
commands with full path, shorten commands such as ls, cd, pwd, and
others. As well manage arguments added to the different commands.


.SH COMMANDS
.TP
All commands passed by the user will be executed as a regular shell would. 

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B ./hsh
.TP
Runs the program normaly allowing the user to enter the desired command during the programs run time.
.TP
.SH
BUILT-IN COMMANDS
.TP
.IP \fBexit\fR
Allows the user to exit our shell interface
.TP
		See \fBman\fR \fIexit\fR for more options.
.TP
.IP \fBenv\fR
Prints out the whole enviroment.
.TP
		See \fBman\fR \fIenv\fR for more options.
.TP
.IP \fBclear\fR
Allows the user to clear the interface
.TP
		 see \ fBman\fR \fIclear\fR for more options.
.TP
.IP \fBhelp\fR
Displays information about
